name: Warp Travel
description:
Warp Travel is a game of skill where you will have to use your reflexes to dodge comets and asteroids by moving your phone.

You are a pilot in a spaceship flying at warp speed trough a lot of asteroids and some comets. Your mission is to survive as long as you can dodging every obstacle in your way by moving your phone to all directions. But beware! the asteroids and comets will increase their speed and quantity the longer you are alive. The game will end when something hits you.

See how many parsecs you can survive and share with your friends!
